FBIS4-36329 "drnes110_g_94002" FBIS-NES-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 Sudan Ministry Supports Yemeni Constitutional Legitimacy Ministry Supports Yemeni Constitutional Legitimacy EA0706205094 Omdurman Republic of Sudan Radio Network in Arabic 1300 GMT 7 Jun 94 EA0706205094 Omdurman Republic of Sudan Radio Network Arabic BFN [Excerpts] Sudan welcomes the visit of U.S. President Bill Clinton's special envoy. [passage omitted] On the current situation in Yemen, the [acting] director of the Political Department in the Foreign Ministry stressed Sudan's stand in favor of constitutional legitimacy in Yemen. He expressed hope that the brothers in Yemen will stop the fighting in order to stop bloodshed. [passage omitted]
